.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span><span class=\"mord\">/2</span></span></span></span> </p>\n<p>So the mathematical language for stating these kinds of scenarios is actually there I just have to figure out how to translate it into lean!</p>",
